strings.Value: "Without the king, goblins need their own hero. Not longshank or halfshank. Their own. Like me."
"That's great, Nok-Nok, keep it up! Maybe someday you'll grow some spine... instead of warts, ha!"
"After the fall of the king the whole tribe should have been gone, like the last breath of life leaving a corpse's lungs. Yet goblins tend to defy universal laws."
